📱 Flutter va Mercure Integration (Qo'llanma)
Ushbu qo'llanma Taxi ilovasida haydovchi qismida Mercure orqali buyurtmalarni real-vaqtda qabul qilish va tariflar bo'yicha filtrlashni o'z ichiga oladi.

1. Bog'liqliklarni o'rnatish (pubspec.yaml)
Loyiha sozlamalariga quyidagi paketlarni qo'shish kerak:

YAML

dependencies:
  flutter:
    sdk: flutter
  mercure_client: ^2.0.0 # Mercure Hub bilan ulanish uchun
  audioplayers: ^5.2.1   # Yangi buyurtma kelganda ovoz chiqarish uchun

flutter:
  assets:
    - assets/sounds/new_order.mp3 # Ovoz fayli yo'li
2. Mercure Xizmati Klassi (lib/services/mercure_service.dart)
Ushbu klass ulanishni boshqaradi, xabarlarni qabul qiladi va haydovchi tanlagan tariflariga mosligini tekshiradi.

Dart

import 'dart:async';
import 'dart:convert';
import 'package:mercure_client/mercure_client.dart';
import 'package:audioplayers/audioplayers.dart';

class MercureService {
  // Singleton pattern
  static final MercureService _instance = MercureService._internal();
  factory MercureService() => _instance;
  MercureService._internal();

  Mercure? _mercure;
  StreamSubscription? _subscription;
  final AudioPlayer _audioPlayer = AudioPlayer();

  bool isConnected = false;

  /// Mercure hub-ga ulanish
  void connect({
    required int companyId,
    required List<String> myActiveTariffs, // Haydovchi yoqqan tariflari: ['start', 'comfort']
    String? jwtToken, // Backend-dan keladigan xavfsizlik tokeni
  }) {
    disconnect(); // Eski ulanishni yopish

    const String hubUrl = 'https://mercure.sizning-serveringiz.uz/.well-known/mercure';
    final String topic = 'company/$companyId/orders/global';

    _mercure = Mercure(
      url: hubUrl,
      topics: [topic],
      token: jwtToken,
    );

    try {
      _subscription = _mercure!.listen().listen(
        (event) {
          isConnected = true;
          _processMessage(event.data, myActiveTariffs);
        },
        onError: (error) {
          isConnected = false;
          print('Mercure Error: $error');
        },
        onDone: () => isConnected = false,
      );
      print('Mercure: $topic kanaliga ulanish o\'rnatildi.');
    } catch (e) {
      print('Mercure Connection Failed: $e');
    }
  }

  /// Kelgan JSON xabarni tahlil qilish
  void _processMessage(String rawData, List<String> myTariffs) {
    try {
      final Map<String, dynamic> data = jsonDecode(rawData);

      // JSON ichidan tarifni ajratib olish
      final String incomingTariff = (data['tariff'] ?? '').toString().toLowerCase();
      
      // Haydovchi tanlagan tariflariga mosligini tekshirish
      bool isMatch = myTariffs.any((t) => t.toLowerCase() == incomingTariff);

      if (isMatch) {
        _playOrderSound();
        print('YANGI BUYURTMA KELDI: ID #${data['orderId']}');
        // Bu yerda UI-da Modal yoki Notification chiqarish funksiyasi chaqiriladi
      } else {
        print('Buyurtma tarifi ($incomingTariff) haydovchiga mos emas.');
      }
    } catch (e) {
      print('JSON Decode Error: $e');
    }
  }

  Future<void> _playOrderSound() async {
    try {
      await _audioPlayer.play(AssetSource('sounds/new_order.mp3'));
    } catch (e) {
      print('Ovoz chiqarishda xato: $e');
    }
  }

  void disconnect() {
    _subscription?.cancel();
    _mercure?.close();
    isConnected = false;
    print('Mercure ulanishi uzildi.');
  }
}
3. Ilovada Ishlatish Namunasi
Haydovchi profilida "Ishga chiqish" tugmasi bosilganda:

Dart

final _mercure = MercureService();

// Online bo'lish
void goOnline() {
  _mercure.connect(
    companyId: 5, // Kompaniya ID
    myActiveTariffs: ['start', 'comfort', 'business'], // Haydovchi tariflari
    // jwtToken: 'backend_bergan_token', 
  );
}

// Offline bo'lish
void goOffline() {
  _mercure.disconnect();
}
💡 Do'stingiz uchun eslatmalar:
JSON Strukturasi: Backend yuborayotgan JSON ichida albatta tariff kaliti bo'lishi kerak.

JWT: Xavfsizlik uchun backend'dan JWT token olish va u orqali ulanish shart.

Background: Ilova yopiq bo'lganda ham xabar kelishi uchun flutter_background_service paketini qo'shish tavsiya etiladi.
